volume.name: I'd Go with the Helmet, Ray: A Doonesbury Book

description: Believe it or not, Archie's quaint little hometown of Riverdale is a celebrity hotspot! Check out the adventures of Archie and the gang as they're visited by some of the hottest and coolest names in pop culture. From music icons to famous chefs to the President of the United States, Archie and the gang get a share of the limelight in over 100 pages of fun! Can Veronica help President Obama stimulate the economy? Will Archie and Colbie Callait make beautiful music together? And what's up with these KISS guys, anyway? Get ready to see some stars!
name: Archie & Friends Seeing Stars!

description: David Masters is a young doctor with an unusual penchant for danger! When someone's in peril, Young Dr. Masters is on the scene and ready to save lives! But his real passion lies with medical research, finding out the cures for deadly diseases. Can he balance his responsibilities as a doctor and a scientist while his father tries to control his fate?
name: The Adventures of Young Dr. Masters The Complete Series

description: WHO is Archie Andrews? A caveman? A Roman emperor? An American Revolutionary soldier? He's all that and more! Join Archie, Jughead, Betty and Veronica on a tour through time as only Archie Comics can give. You'll see the sites in prehistoric times, learn how to rope and ride in the Wild West, and maybe even take a look into life in the year 3000! With over 150 pages of fun, time will fly as you read!
name: Archie Through Time

description: IT'S A MAAAAADHOUSE! Archie is proud to present the best stories from Archie's Madhouse, a series of wild and wacky tales that are sure to leave you laughing and going crazy for more! From the madcap superhero adventures of Captain Sprocket to the antics of Lester Cool and Chester Square and everything in-between, there's something for everyone in this Digital Exclusive. So hit that Download button and get MAD!
name: Archie's Madhouse

description: Get ready -- these crazy tales of monsters and mayhem might leave you batty! Archie Comics presents to you a collection of funny, freaky stories from our vault, all designed to tickle BOTH of your funny bones! Vampires, monsters, werewolves --they're all here, and all totally nuts! This Digital Exclusive collects over 50 spooky, silly pages that'll have you in stitches like the Frankenstein monster himself!
name: Archie's Tales Calculated to Drive You Bats

description: The creatures that go BUMP in the night have invaded Riverdale! It's Halloween time again, and that means the monsters are out and about! Join Archie, Jughead, Betty, Veronica and the whole Riverdale gang as they battle monsters, hang out with witches, and put on some pretty awesome costumes! What kind of weird creatures will they encounter? Do the monster mash with this 100+ page digital exclusive!
name: Archie's Halloween Blowout 2 Rise of the Monsters
